He shared the video on his official Facebook page & claimed it as a world record by captioning the video, "No one has ever played guiter with the sound of washing clothes. I've set a record." Romio consistently shared videos of innovative ways of playing guitar on his Facebook page. He played guitar under the blanket, under his own lungi. He even holds the unique record of playing guitar buried under the sands.
